1\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\"}, {\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghans\", \"score\": 0.8200936471260954, \"rank\": 0.21937293797820712, \"text\": \"Afghan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that moment ended up changing her life, unlocking new possibilities and dreams for the 17-year-old living in Kabul.\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.164477344405221e-18, \"text\": \"Kabul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"new possibilities\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"dreams\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"the 17-year-old living\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three months later, Talash had summoned the courage to visit the gym where the breakdancers, known as theSuperiors Crew, trained, hoping to learn from the person she had seen spinning on his head in the video.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Talash\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"the courage\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakdancers\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"theSuperiors Crew\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were 55 boys, and I was only a girl,\\\" Talash explained.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"55 boys\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"only a girl\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"Talash\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At first, she was hesitant to do anything more than watch the dancers, but as she got to know the breaking community, her concerns disappeared - and her determination to pursue the sport increased.\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancers\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaking community\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"her concerns\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"her determination\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In that gym, gender was not important,\\\" she recalled, speaking fondly of the Superiors Crew.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that gym\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"gender\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"the Superiors Crew\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At school or in my family, they always told me, 'You are a girl.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"a girl\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not do that thing, or that sport, or that job,\\\" she said confidently in perfect Spanish, a language she learned after finding safety in Spain in 2021.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francoist_Spain\", \"score\": 0.9854148651464171, \"rank\": 0.01476363092955694, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francoist_Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francoist_Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that thing\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"perfect Spanish\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"a language\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But within that gym, they always told me, 'You can do it.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that gym\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not impossible.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is difficult, but it is not impossible.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So she got to work, mastering power moves in training and unlocking a wider understanding of hip-hop culture, as well as her place within this dynamic art form.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"power moves\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider understanding\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop culture\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"this dynamic art form\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did this under the watchful eye of her first coach Jawad Sezdah - the very dancer she saw in the online video that ignited her passion in the first place.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jawad_Saleem\", \"score\": 0.9999999986521289, \"rank\": 1.225865987264027e-09, \"text\": \"Jawad\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jawad_Saleem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jawad_Saleem\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the watchful eye\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"her first coach\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"the very dancer\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"the online video\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"her passion\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"the first place\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years later, she is now Afghanistan's first \\\"b-girl\\\", a term to describe female breakdancers.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9992622006418019, \"rank\": 0.0007383441080056664, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a term\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"female breakdancers\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sporting short, choppy hair and a streetwear style, her cool and collected demeanour belies the endless hours of work she put in to achieve her dreams.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"short, choppy hair\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"a streetwear style\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"demeanour belies\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"the endless hours\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"her dreams\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now 21, she's preparing to compete in the Paris Olympic Games, crediting Kabul's close-knit breakdancing community for helping her get there.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1986, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.164477344405221e-18, \"text\": \"Kabul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it has not been an easy journey to the Games.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an easy journey\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The breakdancing gym in Kabul came under attack multiple times, in a country grappling with political and cultural churn where the role of women in public draws particular scrutiny.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.164477344405221e-18, \"text\": \"Kabul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kabul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The breakdancing gym\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"attack\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"political and cultural churn\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"particular scrutiny\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A car bomb exploded outside the venue and in a separate instance, police detained a would-be suicide bomber.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A car bomb\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"a separate instance\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"a would-be suicide bomber\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dancers were left with few options when the club eventually closed over security concerns.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The dancers\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"few options\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"security concerns\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a female breakdancer, Talash also started receiving death threats.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a female breakdancer\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"Talash\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"death threats\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was when she decided to change her name - Talash, the name she adopted, is a Persian word for \\\"striving\\\" - to protect her loved ones from potential danger.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Persian_language\", \"score\": 0.9999998420235112, \"rank\": 1.1326196174986284e-07, \"text\": \"Persian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Persian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Persian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her name - Talash\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2628}, {\"ngram\": \"her loved ones\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"potential danger\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was only afraid for my family,\\\" she calmly explained, maintaining the death threats would not stop her from achieving her dreams.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2858, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"the death threats\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"her dreams\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then things got worse.\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, the Taliban regained control of Afghanistan, bringing with them a controversial new set of crackdowns on women's rights.\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2896, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999997915774874, \"rank\": 2.084227273032919e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}, {\"begin\": 2924, \"end\": 2935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9992622006418019, \"rank\": 0.0007383441080056664, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"a controversial new set\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"crackdowns\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2993}, {\"ngram\": \"women's rights\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talash did not wait for the Taliban to outlawmusicandgirls' educationor strip away their freedom tovisit parks, fairs, and gyms.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3042, \"end\": 3049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.9999997915774874, \"rank\": 2.084227273032919e-07, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Talash\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"outlawmusicandgirls' educationor strip\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"their freedom tovisit parks\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"fairs\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"gyms\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her breakdancing dreams no longer tenable, she fled across the border into Pakistan, taking her 12-year-old brother with her.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.999999990895958, \"rank\": 9.092378791546028e-09, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her breakdancing dreams\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"the border\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3217}, {\"ngram\": \"her 12-year-old brother\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The following year is one that the Olympian said she longs to forget.\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3310, \"end\": 3318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999996267025169, \"rank\": 3.732968343991789e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The following year\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unable to train, separated from her mother and stranded without a passport, she was forced to wait for her case to be processed so she could leave Pakistan for Europe.\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3492, \"end\": 3500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.999999990895958, \"rank\": 9.092378791546028e-09, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"a passport\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3419}, {\"ngram\": \"her case\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was eventually granted asylum in Spain, and found time to sporadically dance while adjusting to her new life and working in a hair salon in the small northern town of Huesca.\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3551, \"end\": 3556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francoist_Spain\", \"score\": 0.9854148651464171, \"rank\": 0.01476363092955694, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francoist_Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francoist_Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"asylum\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"her new life\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"a hair salon\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"the small northern town\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"Huesca\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Talash's friends who refused to let the breakdancer give up hope, desperately reaching out to contacts and sharing Manizha's story in the hopes of catching the attention of prominent sporting organisers.\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3815, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manizha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manizha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://db